## Regression in R: `lm()`, `summary()`, & `tidy()`


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
model1 <- lm(life_expectancy_years_2011 ~ female_literacy_rate_2011,
                 data = gapm)
summary(model1)
```

